installing bootstrap to our project

- pip install django-bootstrap3

- To check if the models were defined properly
        python manage.py check

- Make Migrations
        python manage.py makemigrations news

- view migration(We can view what SQL functions will be called when we run our migration by running the following command.)
        python manage.py sqlmigrate news 0001 (depends on the number assigned to your model when migration is performed)

- Run Migration
        python3.6 manage.py migrate

 - crispy forms
  pip install django-crispy-forms